{"tid":297254,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓右眼好似出左事","createTime":"2017-06-25T10:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T16:50:41.000Z","uid":3811,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93787c154dfe9d1e0607612698869e5426c6f8e5","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，明明佢尋日仲好地地， 今日出完街返屋企例牌同佢深情對望果陣發現佢隻右眼好似怪怪地， 燈光下有啲綠色反光， 之後望真啲佢個角膜好似有啲混濁， 同左眼比好明顯睇唔清虹膜既紋理， 眼白紅根好嚴重， 想問下有冇人知佢發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經book左獸醫聽日去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/175402_e873b749a07cb960f011e8bc3bc32395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F175402_e873b749a07cb960f011e8bc3bc32395.jpg&h=73062900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正常左眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/175436_27a100bf1978a49fdcd18e4157de5164.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F175436_27a100bf1978a49fdcd18e4157de5164.jpg&h=5ef29e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問題右眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/175535_f58c0de81d162b7c7513f196c5833de6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F175535_f58c0de81d162b7c7513f196c5833de6.jpg&h=2cde9b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好明顯右眼有問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/175834_c2b4d57e273dc51b177c342d15450d99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F175834_c2b4d57e273dc51b177c342d15450d99.jpg&h=909f7f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇下佢幾得意， 好擔心啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有經驗可以答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1a28edaf1e6e092519dc26f23d4c866cf86ac7","tid":297254,"uid":38874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ad464a366efe3c09563972dfebf51217024ce32","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青光</blockquote><br />\n應該冇咩可能一日內發展到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdbfc766028274b30ec9bfa8cc83d802aeb6806","tid":297254,"uid":38874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:04:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f99a8379d220bb36350741b7cbfd558bd5744f4","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你平時冇留意</blockquote><br />\n我日日都同佢對望好多次， 所以應該唔會平時冇留意， 係今朝我女朋友發現佢隻眼怪怪地， 佢仲未趕得切同我講我就發現左"},{"pid":"03aa5b15352b3f19a961cc52faeea04d5f2afab3","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"主人龍體欠安啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c963be77043a3ed7695f6f64e0e5ff8bc697d2","tid":297254,"uid":82373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"有過濾性病毒，去獸醫度滴 D 藥水再照紫光燈就睇到，冇得根治，好似人 D 泡疹病毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb51cc4afa7611f1fa463f7fd83e84b54b75b5d7","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有過濾性病毒，去獸醫度滴 D 藥水再照紫光燈就睇到，冇得根治，好似人 D 泡疹病毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係家貓由細到大都冇出過街， 連屋企門口都好少行近"},{"pid":"9e7b91d8bb9f603a31c86392e5d710cef5cdfeea","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d79e8d4433f22ee619e629f196334a6275102f8","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a987b02250c7d3e8ca98733937969acb73fb4564","tid":297254,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423ff1053874317c1bccaa83f5ccc788fa8f788b","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbebc14c2f1d7e6de27b4ce4290cd23c43d89e5b","tid":297254,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有過濾性病毒，去獸醫度滴 D 藥水再照紫光燈就睇到，冇得根治，好似人 D 泡疹病毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係家貓由細到大都冇出過街， 連屋企門口都好少行近</blockquote><br />\n人會帶入屋架嘛但係"},{"pid":"d40d2a20a3138507a1e4a87d0d755a406e297d55","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忍唔住帶左佢去24/7既動物醫院， 等緊， 希望佢冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6cad2cd1f6ac2b9ca4eeca76bbf4071a6943c9","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有過濾性病毒，去獸醫度滴 D 藥水再照紫光燈就睇到，冇得根治，好似人 D 泡疹病毒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但佢係家貓由細到大都冇出過街， 連屋企門口都好少行近</blockquote><br />\n人會帶入屋架嘛但係</blockquote><br />\n都有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51f375d3ef23c13eba17f7a10360adf33062f16","tid":297254,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"樓主點呀"},{"pid":"a70d06009a26523e1912f9fe01925d236240b4b3","tid":297254,"uid":82373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T00:59:42.000Z","msg":"唔會有生命危險，D病毒潛伏係神經末稍，抵抗力差時會返發，留意多 D同早 D滴抗病毒眼藥水就可控制。"},{"pid":"a635121d53c848eb4036b2374742955f8d3a5df7","tid":297254,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主點呀</blockquote><br />\nupdate返， 醫生話佢隻眼係外傷， 眼角膜損左少少， 有機會係玩既時候整親或者自己抓到自己<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢有少少上呼吸道感染， 但已經係差唔多好返， 只係有啲牙肉紅腫， 藥都唔洗食<br />\n<br />\n啲病毒有可能係朋友隻貓度傳比佢， 都係啲好常見既病毒， 未完全病發就已經好左（佢齊曬針， 各位記得帶主人去打針）<br />\n<br />\n而家每日隻眼要搽藥， 3-5日就會完全康復<br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係張bill, 係澳洲, after hours要額外收300aud， 埋單差唔多400aud<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50b28e5eaa298cd04bd39153c8e37b33eab3e98","tid":297254,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T02:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主點呀</blockquote><br />\nupdate返， 醫生話佢隻眼係外傷， 眼角膜損左少少， 有機會係玩既時候整親或者自己抓到自己<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢有少少上呼吸道感染， 但已經係差唔多好返， 只係有啲牙肉紅腫， 藥都唔洗食<br />\n<br />\n啲病毒有可能係朋友隻貓度傳比佢， 都係啲好常見既病毒， 未完全病發就已經好左（佢齊曬針， 各位記得帶主人去打針）<br />\n<br />\n而家每日隻眼要搽藥， 3-5日就會完全康復<br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係張bill, 係澳洲, after hours要額外收300aud， 埋單差唔多400aud<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n錢財身外物, 貓貓無事就好"},{"pid":"9dca68d995de89c10852df6a6ba70a0d63bae11c","tid":297254,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主點呀</blockquote><br />\nupdate返， 醫生話佢隻眼係外傷， 眼角膜損左少少， 有機會係玩既時候整親或者自己抓到自己<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢有少少上呼吸道感染， 但已經係差唔多好返， 只係有啲牙肉紅腫， 藥都唔洗食<br />\n<br />\n啲病毒有可能係朋友隻貓度傳比佢， 都係啲好常見既病毒， 未完全病發就已經好左（佢齊曬針， 各位記得帶主人去打針）<br />\n<br />\n而家每日隻眼要搽藥， 3-5日就會完全康復<br />\n<br />\n唯一問題係張bill, 係澳洲, after hours要額外收300aud， 埋單差唔多400aud<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港好似都係咁貴？<br />\n貓貓平安就好"}]}